## About Software Commons

Software Commons **sustainably shares society's software**, both [Open Source
Projects][3] and [Open Products][4]. We celebrate sustainable software sharing
in all forms.

Read more [about Software Commons][8].

[2]: https://chat.openai.com/share/f6a2f760-f3e8-485d-a61e-ff834cbc95d3
